          <h2 style="             
              font-size: 20px;
              line-height: 1.2;
              font-weight: 500;
              margin-top: 2px !important;">Black Swan’s author warns Nvidia crash is just the start</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.longandshort.com/email/images/ls-jan-29-1.png" alt="Black Swan’s author warns Nvidia crash is just the start" href="https://www.altdaily.co" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4">Author of The Black Swan, Nassim Taleb, has warned that <a href="https://link.longandshort.com/ls-29-01-2025-nvidia-big-drop" target="_blank">Nvidia’s big drop</a> might start a broader market correction. Taleb suggests that the declines could be two or three times larger as investors continue to evaluate the risks attached to the AI market. Taleb is an advisor to a tail-risk hedge fund and maintains that investors often underestimate the dangers connected to tech stocks. Taleb also raised concerns about the US debt levels, the increasing labor costs, and Trump’s tariffs that could lead to an ‘explosion of inflation.’</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
